// Calcul de l'âge le plus fréquent sur une plage d'âges (mode/valeur dominante)
val agesMode = usersWithRange.groupBy("ageRange", "age").agg(
        count("age").as("sameAgeCount")
        )
        
val ageMeans = agesMode
    .groupBy("ageRange").agg(
        max("sameAgeCount").as("maxCount"),
        round(mean(col("age"))).as("meanAge")
    ).select(col("maxCount"), col("meanAge"))
    
val ageModeFull = agesMode.join(ageMeans, agesMode("sameAgeCount") === ageMeans("maxCount")).select(col("ageRange"), col("age").as("ageMode"), col("meanAge"))

z.show(ageModeFull)
